title: The Who - Quadrophenia Live In London [320k MP3] NYC
description:
Quadrophenia Live in London is a live release from British rock band, The Who. It documents their 8 July 2013 concert at London's Wembley Arena, the final show of their 2013 tour and their last show to date. It is available as a double-CD album, DVD, Blu-ray and deluxe box set and was released on 9 June 2014.
